      • classify

        Map<String,Classification> classify(IDataWindow<DATA> sample)
                             throws AISPException
        Get the classification(s) of the given data window. This method must be thread-safe and if need-be the implementation should add synchronization if required.
        Parameters:
        sample - data to be classified.
        Returns:
        a map of label names to Classification instances.
        Throws:
        AISPException - if not trained.
